summary: Example test for using multiple artifact providers
description: |
    Demonstrates how to use multiple artifact providers together
    in a single prepare step.

    Example usage:
        prepare:
          - how: artifact
            provide:
              - koji.build:2625600
              - repository-url:https://example.com/repo.repo

    This test shows:
    - How to combine different provider types
    - Multiple --provide arguments in one prepare step
    - Packages from different sources work together
tag+:
  - provision-only
  - provision-container
adjust:
  - when: distro != fedora
    enabled: false
    because: Test uses Fedora-specific providers
